   RUSSIA-CHECHNYA (Mozdok, Russia) _ Mikhail A. Kashpurin is a
frail old man with years of valorous service in the Soviet army, an
unblemished labor record and a story to tell. It boils down to
this. He was in the wrong place at the wrong time. The place was
Grozny and the time was Russia's ongoing military campaign. By
Michael R. Gordon.
