throughout the year. But there is little call for frosted elms in
July.
</P>
<P>
   This clever company has, however, found a neat solution: an
equivalent but opposite seasonal product.
</P>
<P>
   In the off months, its Shenzhen elves now make rather spiffy
garden furniture in a new factory next to its tree workshop. &QL; 
